          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Q:</strong> What’s your best-selling masterpiece?</p><p><strong>A: </strong>My emotional support pickles. (But sometimes my dishcloths and dog bandanas).</p><p><strong>— Olivia, age 11</strong></p><p></p>",
